casebody.head_matter:
Michael Charles SMITH, Petitioner,
v.
FLORIDA.
No. 19-7310.
Supreme Court of the United States.
March 23, 2020
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until April 13, 2020, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
